BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Connect Mat-Su": "https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/free-training-youth-carpentry-mat-su/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:connect_matsu
X-SOURCE:Connect Mat-Su
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260309T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260313T163000
DTSTAMP:20260308T083557
CREATED:20260127T112212Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260308T162210Z
UID:10012797-1773043200-1773419400@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:Free Training Youth Carpentry: Mat-Su
DESCRIPTION:FREE Youth Carpentry Training – Mat-Su!\nLooking for something awesome (and productive!) to do over Spring Break?  Join Alaska Works Partnership for a FREE weeklong Youth Carpentry Training in Wasilla!\n Spring Break training is available to any high school age students.\n Learn carpentry basics + trades math\n Practice measuring/layout skills\n Tool safety + hands-on experience\n Build real projects (footstool + coffee table!)\n Get jobsite-ready and explore construction careers\n March 9–13\, 2026 (Mon–Fri)\n 8:00 AM – 4:30 PM\n 619 S Knik Goose Bay Rd\, Unit E – Wasilla\n Call: 907-376-4704\n alaskaworks.org\n Spots are limited\, apply today!
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/free-training-youth-carpentry-mat-su/
END:VEVENT
