BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/jr-ski-patrol-day-ages-9-15/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260309T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260309T130000
DTSTAMP:20260308T083559
CREATED:20260221T160838Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T160838Z
UID:7988-1773050400-1773061200@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:Jr Ski Patrol Day • Ages 9–15
DESCRIPTION:Our first Junior Ski Patrol Day booked up in only 3 days! Due to the demand we’ve created this third day\, for ages 9-15\, for those who may have missed out! Be sure to register ahead of time as spaces fill up quickly.\nJr Ski Patrol Day is for kids/young teens who are interested in learning more about skills needed to be a ski patroller including mountain setup\, toboggan demo\, first aid\, and avalanche rescue skills. Participants can expect to be outdoors and on skis/snowboards during the day\, so be sure to dress accordingly.\n13500 N. Skeetawk Circle\, Palmer
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/jr-ski-patrol-day-ages-9-15/
END:VEVENT
