BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/winter-ladies-only-outing-cold-weather-kayaking/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260314T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260314T170000
DTSTAMP:20260308T083559
CREATED:20260106T000021Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260106T000021Z
UID:7002-1773478800-1773507600@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:Winter Ladies’ Only Outing (Cold Weather Kayaking)
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a Ladies’ Only Cold-Weather Kayaking Adventure!\nLadies\, let’s embrace the crisp air\, stunning winter light\, and pure Alaska magic from the water! We’ll kick things off with a quick safety briefing at the Eklutna Tailrace—then we’re launching into a one-of-a-kind kayaking experience that’s peaceful\, powerful\, and absolutely unforgettable.\nWe’ve got you covered with a warming area\, steaming hot cocoa\, and fresh pastries. Your local\, experienced guides will be right by your side\, making sure you feel confident and inspired the entire time.\nCan’t make this month’s ladies-only adventure?\nNo worries—more chances to get outside together are on the way:\nFuture monthly adventures: Stay tuned for releases!\nAdventure\, connection\, and some serious cold-weather magic—let’s make it happen!
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/winter-ladies-only-outing-cold-weather-kayaking/
END:VEVENT
