X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/palmer-alehouse-unplugged-mel-and-friends/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260326T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260326T210000
DTSTAMP:20260308T083559
CREATED:20260221T162306Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T162701Z
UID:7998-1774548000-1774558800@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:Palmer Alehouse Unplugged: Mel and Friends
DESCRIPTION:This is a FREE all ages show with limited seating. Attendees under 21 must be accompanied by a parent or guardian.\nJoin us in the Upstairs Lounge every Thursday for our winter live music series featuring stripped down performances from some of our favorite artists from the big stage!\nMel & Friends delivers an intimate acoustic night led by longtime Alaska singer-songwriter Melissa Mitchell. Known for her honest songwriting and soulful voice\, Mitchell blends folk and Americana with stories drawn from life in Alaska\, joined by musical friends for a relaxed\, heartfelt evening of songs and connection.\nPalmer Ale House 320 E. Dahlia Avenue\, Palmer\, AK
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/palmer-alehouse-unplugged-mel-and-friends/
END:VEVENT
