BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Connect Mat-Su": "https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/2026-kickoff-kitchen/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:connect_matsu
X-SOURCE:Connect Mat-Su
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260424T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260424T200000
DTSTAMP:20260308T083557
CREATED:20260227T010534Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260308T162208Z
UID:10012846-1777050000-1777060800@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:2026 Kickoff Kitchen
DESCRIPTION:Tickets for our 2026 Kickoff Kitchen fundraiser and annual Community Awards are ON SALE NOW!\nJoin us for this celebration of local volunteers\, businesses and community champions\, and our past year’s accomplishments. We are excited for another great event\, and to announce our Volunteer of the Year\, Dorothy A. Jones Lifetime Achievement Award\, Business Partner of the Year and Community Champion award winners.\nBring your best bidding face for our Live Auction\, try NOT to be outbid on the incredible desserts in our Dessert Auction\, and test your knowledge with Kathy’s trivia contest!  \n$70 individual\n$400 for a table of 6 \nSpecial thanks to Mat-Su Health Foundations \nQuestions? Please call (907)745-5822 or email give@unitedwaymatsu.org
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/2026-kickoff-kitchen/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=application/pdf:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Kitchen-Kickoff.pdf
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/2026-kickoff-kitchen-moving-mountains-together/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260424T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260424T190000
DTSTAMP:20260308T083559
CREATED:20260221T165702Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T165702Z
UID:8018-1777050000-1777057200@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:2026 Kickoff Kitchen: Moving Mountains Together
DESCRIPTION:Join United Way of Mat-Su for our annual celebration of community\, giving and volunteerism.Presentation of our Dorothy A. Jones Lifetime Achievement\, Volunteer of the Year\, Community Champion and Business Partner of the Year awards will take place during the event program.Bring your sweet tooth and bid on AMAZING handmade desserts at our Dessert Auction! Live auction to follow formal program.Enjoy hearty passed appetizers catered by the Mat-Su Career Tech Culinary Team and local brews from Bleeding Heart Brewery.$70 individual or $400 for a table of 6.Questions? Please call (907)745-5822 or email give@ unitedwaymatsu.org.**Desserts and live auction items/packages are still needed!** \nThe Government Peak Chalet\, 10690 N. Mountain Trails Dr. Palmer \n 
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/2026-kickoff-kitchen-moving-mountains-together/
END:VEVENT
