X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/plant-sale-by-palmer-ffa/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260508
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260510
DTSTAMP:20260308T083559
CREATED:20260221T170928Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T170928Z
UID:8028-1778198400-1778371199@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:Plant Sale by Palmer FFA
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Palmer FFA’s annual plant sale! We always open Mother’s Day weekend\, 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM Friday and Saturday\, at the Palmer High School Agriculture Building. Come get your annuals\, hanging baskets\, strawberries\, and veggies galore! If we don’t sell out\, we’ll be open a second weekend. Don’t miss out on a great event and supporting your local FFA chapter! \nPalmer High\, 1170 W. Bogard Rd. Palmer \n 
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/plant-sale-by-palmer-ffa/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/alaska-vintage-spring-market-food-truck-fest-enchanted-garden-theme/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260508
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260511
DTSTAMP:20260308T083559
CREATED:20260221T171212Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T171212Z
UID:8031-1778198400-1778457599@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:Alaska Vintage Spring Market & Food Truck Fest "Enchanted Garden Theme"
DESCRIPTION:Come enjoy a fun weekend with friends and family! Shop some of Alaska’s trendiest small businesses\, up-cyclers\, designers\, and vintage collectors! We are also throwing a food truck festival with over 30 food vendors/truck. It’s going to be a blast! We love supporting other local Alaskan businesses and we hope you can come out and support them as well!\nThe first 100 VIP (weekend pass $10 EACH DAY bag with goodies)\nFriday 12-6 $5Saturday 10-6 $5Sunday 10-4 FreeTICKETS will be available soon.\nAlaska State Fairgrounds
