CREATED:20250528T001755Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260308T162209Z
UID:10012611-1780221600-1780221600@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:Coffee w/ A Veteran
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Saturday morning and get loud at 10am for Coffee with a Veteran! It’s always an interesting series of discussions and it ends whenever the “good ‘ol boys” shovel off!\nFREE coffee and locally procured donuts\nWhether you’re a Veteran or not\, all are invited to hang out and chat.
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/coffee-w-a-veteran-2/
END:VEVENT
